scene.message:
Yukino: What an over-the-top{nl}
door. That showy feel is{nl}
so Michiko{waitkey}it makes me sick!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: I wonder if that{nl}
Michiko played "the Snow{nl}
Queen" once too~{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hmph! A door as{nl}
unpleasant as that woman!{nl}
All flashy surface{waitkey}with nothing inside!{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: I'd love to take this{nl}
back to my room! Mm-hm, a{nl}
stylish door.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Umm... it's a bit too{nl}
obvious for a Trap door,{nl}
isn't it.{waitkey}{ret}
